OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,FSeveral families who lost loved ones
OL,7,Fin the Creeslough explosion have
OL,8,Fcalled on the Irish Government to set
OL,9,Fup a public inquiry into the tragedy.
OL,11,FA lawyer representing the next of kin
OL,12,Fof seven of the 10 victims of the
OL,13,FOctober 2022 blast in the Co Donegal
OL,14,Fvillage have written to Minister for
OL,15,FJustice Helen McEntee asking for an
OL,16,Findependent investigation to be
OL,17,Festablished.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
