OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,FTheir request comes as gardai continue
OL,7,Fto investigate the circumstances of
OL,8,Fthe explosion that ripped through the
OL,9,Fvillage's Applegreen service station
OL,10,Fand a nearby apartment block on the
OL,11,Fafternoon of Friday October 7.
OL,13,FFour men, three women and three
OL,14,Fchildren, ranging in age from five to
OL,15,F59, died in the blast.
OL,17,FWhile the cause of the explosion has
OL,18,Fyet to be formally confirmed by the
OL,19,Fauthorities, it is understood a gas
OL,20,Fleak is considered a central line of
OL,21,Finquiry.
