OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,FThose who died were Robert Garwe and
OL,7,Fhis five-year-old daughter Shauna
OL,8,FFlanagan-Garwe; Catherine O'Donnell
OL,9,Fand her 13-year-old son James
OL,10,FMonaghan; fashion student Jessica
OL,11,FGallagher; Celtic fan Martin McGill;
OL,12,FSydney native James O'Flaherty; shop
OL,13,Fworker Martina Martin; carpenter Hugh
OL,14,F"Hughie" Kelly; and 14-year-old Leona
OL,15,FHarper.
OL,17,FPhoenix Law, which acts for the
OL,18,Fmajority of the families, has now
OL,19,Fwritten to Ms McEntee formally seeking
OL,20,Fa public inquiry or commission of
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@HO]
