OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,FDarragh Mackin, solicitor for the
OL,7,Ffamilies, said they had also requested
OL,8,Fa meeting with the minister.
OL,10,FThe letter, seen by the PA news
OL,11,Fagency, said the tragedy of Creeslough
OL,12,Fhad been compounded by the absence of
OL,13,Fan independent human-rights compliant
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FMr Mackin represents next of kin of
OL,17,FRobert Garwe, Shauna Flanagan-Garwe,
OL,18,FCatherine O'Donnell, James Monaghan,
OL,19,FJessica Gallagher, Martina Martin and
OL,20,FLeona Harper.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
