OL,6,FIt said there remained uncertainty
OL,7,Fover when that will conclude and
OL,8,Fwhether it will result in any criminal
OL,9,Fjustice proceedings.
OL,11,FMr Mackin said the statutory function
OL,12,Fof the gardai is to investigate
OL,13,Falleged criminality.
OL,15,F"They cannot be criticised for this
OL,16,Flimitation," he added.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@LO]
