OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Mackin said the Garda was
OL,7,Funable to produce a public report into
OL,8,Fthe incident, disclose documents to
OL,9,Ffamilies or make recommendations to
OL,10,Fensure a similar event never happens
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,13,FHe added: "It is clear on any reading
OL,14,Fthat there are wider issues of
OL,15,Fpreventability relating to the
OL,16,FCreeslough explosion which will
OL,17,Finevitably fall outside the Garda
OL,18,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@uD@KOUzD@OO]
