OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,FIn regard to other types of
OL,7,Finvestigation, the families' solicitor
OL,8,Fsaid there were several reasons why an
OL,9,Finquest would be "insufficient and
OL,10,Fineffective" in the Creeslough case,
OL,11,Fincluding the fact that it could take
OL,12,Fseveral years to be held.
OL,14,FMr Mackin said it was widely
OL,15,Facknowledged, both within and outside
OL,16,Fthe state, that "complex and
OL,17,Fcontentious deaths" require a parallel
OL,18,Finvestigation while a criminal
OL,19,Finvestigation is ongoing.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@LO]xD@QOUyD@SO]
