OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,FHe said the recent inquiry into the
OL,7,FGrenfell fire in London was an "apt
OL,8,Fanalogy" as it took place alongside
OL,9,Fthe police investigation.
OL,11,FIn conclusion, Mr Mackin wrote: "In
OL,12,Flight of the above, we write to
OL,13,Fformally request that the minister
OL,14,Fgive consideration to the
OL,15,Fcommissioning of an independent
OL,16,Finvestigation in the form of a public
OL,17,Finquiry or commission of
OL,18,Finvestigation, in the terms to be
OL,19,Fagreed in consultation with the
OL,20,Ffamilies.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@HO]sD@aOU
