OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,F"The holding of such an investigation
OL,7,Fnow will ensure that no further time
OL,8,Fis lost and indeed will provide our
OL,9,Fclients with a vehicle for getting to
OL,10,Fthe truth and, in turn, finally being
OL,11,Fable to grieve for their loved ones.
OL,13,F"Given the nature of our request, we
OL,14,Fwrite to formally ask the minister to
OL,15,Fconsider meeting with our clients to
OL,16,Fdiscuss this request in more detail at
OL,17,Fyour earliest convenience.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
