OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,F"Finally, as you will appreciate, we
OL,7,Fare now approaching the second
OL,8,Fanniversary and as such we would be
OL,9,Fgrateful if this request could be
OL,10,Fconsidered at your earliest
OL,11,Fconvenience."
OL,13,FA statement from the minister's
OL,14,Fdepartment confirmed she had received
OL,15,Fthe letter and was "currently
OL,16,Fconsidering its contents".
OL,18,F"It would not be appropriate to
OL,19,Fcomment further given there is an
OL,20,Fongoing investigation under way," the
OL,21,Fdepartment added.
