OL,6,FIn a statement, the Garda said: "The
OL,7,Finvestigation, led by gardai in
OL,8,FDonegal division, is ongoing with the
OL,9,Fintention of submitting a file to the
OL,10,FOffice of the Director of Public
OL,11,FProsecutions.
OL,13,F"An Garda Siochana has no further
OL,14,Fcomment at this time."
OL,16,FMr Mackin said the families were
OL,17,Feagerly awaiting a reply from the
OL,18,Fminister.
OL,26,@nD@aOUuD@AOUvD@VO]
