OL,3,CCreeslough families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into explosion
OL,6,F"When horrendous events like this
OL,7,Foccur, there is an imperative need for
OL,8,Fan investigation separate to any
OL,9,Fcriminal process.
OL,11,F"Akin to Grenfell, these families
OL,12,Frequire an independent forum which
OL,13,Fprovides them, and the wider public,
OL,14,Fthe answers that are deserved.
OL,16,F"These families now eagerly await to
OL,17,Fhear from the Minister for Justice on
OL,18,Ftheir request for a meeting and the
OL,19,Fneed for a public inquiry."
